decks.notes: This Pioneer 1 vs 1 deck revolves around the aggressive playstyle of Arclight Phoenix. It focuses on quickly casting spells to generate card advantage and fill up the graveyard, enabling the resurrection of Arclight Phoenix from the graveyard. The deck includes a wide range of cheap spells like Fiery Impulse, Lightning Axe, and Spikefield Hazard to control the board and protect the Phoenix. It also utilizes card draw spells like Opt, Chart a Course, and Treasure Cruise to ensure a steady flow of spells to cast. The deck's land base includes a mix of dual lands to support its mana requirements.
